Pyrogenesis has to be run from /usr/local/bin (wrapper script?)

Doesn't respect CXXFLAGS, etc.

Doesn't (yet) work with spidermonkey-17, see:
http://www.wildfiregames.com/forum/index.php?showtopic=17289
http://trac.wildfiregames.com/ticket/1886

Not linked properly against internal spidermonkey, needs LD_PRELOAD
